{"tid":2343424,"cid":28,"subCid":0,"title":"請轉介社福部門跟進此題目","createTime":"2020-12-28T02:50:25.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-03T14:44:48.000Z","uid":357591,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"bb3716e7c11812791118fdd331f7e6a311add4f7","tid":2343424,"uid":357591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T02:50:25.000Z","msg":"我俾人圍毆<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2333044/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2333044/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n樓主明顯有嚴重精神病+溝通障礙+暴力傾向<br />\n未來很可能會演變為家庭倫常慘劇或隨機殺人事件<br />\n<br />\n希望連登管理人員可以轉介此個案至相關政府社福機構跟進"},{"pid":"2072aac47a49325209d388dfb503a9f7594daee6","tid":2343424,"uid":364666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T05:30:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e741d4e2b5c46b308a96ba62bee402688d43c288","tid":2343424,"uid":364666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T05:35:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0d33f19c98596efe1c17d115797b24cf15c48278","tid":2343424,"uid":268516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T23:35:13.000Z","msg":"介紹佢識李國永"},{"pid":"910f9304e70b5590dfc836a2ec8e2564f4da200c","tid":2343424,"uid":242102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T15:09:32.000Z","msg":"班長點解唔反省自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af37c88783faa26ca60eac177a39cd676b261f60","tid":2343424,"uid":242102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T14:44:48.000Z","msg":"你煩不煩<br />\n成日ff<br />\n受害者妄想<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇下精神科好wor<br />\n<span class=\"gold\"><span class=\"large\">下文供你參考<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<blockquote>精神分裂症因長期被污名化，使許多患者不願就醫<span class=\"gold\">（去睇醫生啦DCC001，起碼Dr_MK冇思覺失調，呢樣佢好過你）</span>，台灣在2014年已正名為「思覺失調症」。<br />\n精神分裂症是一種慢性且重大的精神疾病，與腦內功能運作失常有關，特別是與<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span class=\"green\">一般人的現實有著明顯的脫節</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，以幻聽最為常見，<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span class=\"teal\">患者很清楚聽到有人在和他對話，但旁邊根本沒有其他人</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，或病患深受聽覺的控制，按照某個聲音去殺人或自殺等,也<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span class=\"red\"><span class=\"x-large\">可能出現被害妄想，總覺得有人在某處監視他並打算加害於他</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，因而過度恐慌,也可能<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/discover.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span class=\"orange\">重複一些怪異的舉止</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/discover.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，突然間表現得很退縮、不與任何人互動，某些精神分裂患者還會出現暴力的攻擊行為、無緣無故的<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span class=\"pink\">傻笑、大哭</span>。</blockquote>"}]}